<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="About EcomSphere - Our Heritage, Values and Mission">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/db75cd62a8.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --classic-teal: #088178;
      --classic-dark: #1a1a1a;
      --classic-text: #465b52;
      --classic-bg: #f5f7f9;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Spartan', sans-serif;
    }

    /* Hero Section - Classic High-End */
    #page-header.about-header {
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url("/img/about/banner.png");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      height: 50vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    #page-header h2 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    #page-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #ddd;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Main Content Styling */
    .about-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .about-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
    }

    .about-row:nth-child(even) {
      flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }

    .about-img {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-img img {
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(8, 129, 120, 0.2);
      border: 8px solid #fff;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .about-text {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .about-text span {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--classic-teal);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .about-text h2 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: var(--classic-teal);
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .about-text p {
      color: var(--classic-text);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Features / Stats Bar */
    .classic-stats {
      background: var(--classic-teal);
      padding: 60px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .stat-box h3 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .stat-box p {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      opacity: 0.8;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    /* Heritage Section */
    .heritage-section {
      padding: 100px 20px;
      background-color: var(--classic-bg);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .heritage-section h2 {
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .heritage-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .heritage-card {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .heritage-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }

    .heritage-card i {
      font-size: 40px;
      color: var(--classic-teal);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .heritage-card h4 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: var(--classic-dark);
    }

    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .about-row, .about-row:nth-child(even) {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .about-img, .about-text {
        width: 100%;
      }
      #page-header h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      .classic-stats {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 30px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('./partials/header') %>

  <!-- Classic Hero -->
  <section id="page-header" class="about-header">
    <h2>Our Heritage</h2>
    <p>Defined by quality, driven by passion since 2015.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="about-container">
    <!-- Story Row 1 -->
    <div class="about-row">
      <div class="about-img">
        <img src="/img/about/about.jpg" alt="About US" onerror="this.src='/img/placeholder.jpg'">
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <span>The Journey</span>
        <h2>Redefining Elegant E-Commerce Architecture</h2>
        <p>EcomSphere began with a singular vision: to create a digital boutique that feels as premium as the products it houses. We recognized a gap in the market for a platform that balances technical excellence with aesthetic sophistication.</p>
        <p>Today, we serve a global community of style-conscious individuals who demand transparency, speed, and uncompromising quality in every interaction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <div class="classic-stats">
      <div class="stat-box">
        <h3>10k+</h3>
        <p>Happy Customers</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <h3>50+</h3>
        <p>Premium Brands</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <h3>24h</h3>
        <p>Global Support</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <h3>100%</h3>
        <p>Secure Systems</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Heritage / Values Section -->
  <section class="heritage-section">
    <div class="about-container">
      <h2>The Pillars of EcomSphere</h2>
      <div class="heritage-grid">
        <div class="heritage-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-gem"></i>
          <h4>Uncompromising Quality</h4>
          <p>Every product in our catalog undergoes a rigorous selection process. If it doesn't meet our standards for craftsmanship, it doesn't make it to our store.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="heritage-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
          <h4>Built on Trust</h4>
          <p>Security is the foundation of digital commerce. We utilize military-grade encryption to ensure your data and transactions remain private and protected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="heritage-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-earth-americas"></i>
          <h4>Global Vision</h4>
          <p>Style knows no borders. We've optimized our logistics network to provide fast, reliable shipping to every corner of the globe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Classic Newsletter Integration -->
  <section id="newsletter" class="section-p1 section-m1">
    <div class="newstext">
      <h4>Refined Updates</h4>
      <p>Subscribe to our newsletter for exclusive insights and <span>curated collections.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="form">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Your professional email address">
      <button class="normal">Join Now</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
